    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>The Dire Draugr Wolf is the pack leader of the blind draugr wolves — a massive undead wolf, twice the size of its packmates, with scarred frost-black hide and glowing ice-blue eyes that still burn with predatory command. It coordinates its pack through howls and presence, granting all allies within range advantage on their attacks. Its own Frenzied Bite can chain into multiple consecutive attacks against the same or adjacent targets. The Dire Draugr Wolf does not merely hunt — it orchestrates.</p>",
